No, I wish I did.

17:05.357 --> 17:08.777
I don't have any nice memories
of my father anymore.

17:08.861 --> 17:10.112
Why not?

17:10.194 --> 17:12.781
Did you know
I was the one who found him

17:12.865 --> 17:14.407
the night he killed himself?

17:16.201 --> 17:18.119
I had no idea.

17:18.203 --> 17:20.289
{\an3}Yeah, it was
really horrible.

17:20.372 --> 17:22.624
His brains were
all over the bathroom wall.

17:22.708 --> 17:25.294
{\an1}Val, are you sure you want
to talk about this?

17:25.377 --> 17:27.755
Yeah, I have to.

17:29.048 --> 17:31.258
David's mother, huh?

17:31.341 --> 17:34.344
Yeah, bad luck for me.

17:37.347 --> 17:40.976
I was in the wrong place
at the wrong time.

17:41.059 --> 17:43.479
You know, it took me
a whole year afterwards

17:43.562 --> 17:46.190
to... be able to sleep
through the whole night

17:46.273 --> 17:50.486
and... and now I'm right back
in that place again.

