21:05.305 --> 21:07.349
Please don't leave me.

21:07.432 --> 21:09.518
Okay, I'm right here...

21:09.601 --> 21:11.812
It's gonna be okay.

21:12.938 --> 21:14.523
It's gonna be okay.

21:15.899 --> 21:18.318
{\an3}Get your hands off
the mushrooms, Bruno.

21:18.402 --> 21:20.195
{\an3}You better be nice
to me, Antonia,

21:20.278 --> 21:22.864
or I'm gonna tell your father
you're throwing a dinner party

21:22.948 --> 21:24.074
without asking
his permission.

21:24.157 --> 21:26.076
I am so tired of this, Bruno.

21:26.159 --> 21:27.202
I'm 20 years old.

21:27.285 --> 21:28.578
This <i> is</i> my house.

21:28.662 --> 21:30.580
When is my father
gonna stop checking out

21:30.664 --> 21:32.207
everyone I have
a hamburger with?

21:32.290 --> 21:34.710
{\an3}I've been watching you
with this McKay boy.

21:34.793 --> 21:36.378
You're getting
too involved.

21:36.461 --> 21:38.338
Then stop watching.

21:42.968 --> 21:44.219
Hello?

21:44.302 --> 21:45.512
Hello, sweetheart.

21:45.595 --> 21:47.347
Hi, Daddy.
What are you doing calling me

21:47.431 --> 21:48.557
in the middle of the day?

21:48.640 --> 21:50.058
Are you playing hooky?

21:50.142 --> 21:51.768
Well, actually, I've been
in meeting after meeting.

21:51.852 --> 21:53.729
But you've been
on my mind all day, and...

21:53.812 --> 21:55.063
I wanted to hear your voice.

21:55.147 --> 21:56.773
You holding down
the fort for me?

21:56.857 --> 21:58.233
Everything's fine.

21:58.317 --> 21:59.401
When are you coming home?

21:59.484 --> 22:00.944
Well, hopefully, tomorrow night.

22:01.028 --> 22:03.071
