Bring me something?

22:03.155 --> 22:04.156
Don't I always?

22:04.239 --> 22:05.115
Yes.

22:05.198 --> 22:06.241
I love you, Dad.

22:06.324 --> 22:07.409
I love you, too, sweetheart.

22:07.492 --> 22:08.577
And I miss you.

22:08.660 --> 22:09.745
I miss you, too.

22:09.828 --> 22:12.039
See you tomorrow.

22:14.374 --> 22:17.169
Toni, listen to me.

22:17.252 --> 22:18.420
{\an1}There are things
about this boy

22:18.503 --> 22:19.588
that you don't know.

22:19.671 --> 22:21.256
{\an1}There are things
about this boy

22:21.339 --> 22:23.425
{\an1}that are not gonna make
your father happy.

22:23.508 --> 22:26.178
{\an3}Then don't tell
him, Bruno.

22:26.261 --> 22:28.930
{\an6}Ms. Marchette,
Mr. McKay is here
to see you.

22:29.014 --> 22:30.599
He's out at the pool.

22:30.682 --> 22:31.808
Thank you, Douglas.

22:39.649 --> 22:41.485
