a lot of work.

22:53.163 --> 22:54.915
{\an1}Why don't you try
it sometime?

22:54.998 --> 22:56.750
{\an3}'Cause I'd rather try
something else.

22:56.833 --> 22:58.877
{\an1}What?

22:58.960 --> 23:00.670
{\an3}Well, to be
perfectly honest...

23:03.924 --> 23:05.842
{\an1}(squeals)

23:05.926 --> 23:06.968
{\an1}(laughs)

23:17.604 --> 23:21.650
♪ Loving you is my destination ♪

23:21.733 --> 23:23.318
♪ Keep on pushing... ♪

23:23.401 --> 23:24.486
Oh, can you believe that?

23:24.569 --> 23:27.322
{\an4}That little stinker
took the bait out
of all the traps.

23:27.405 --> 23:28.824
I know he's down there.

23:28.907 --> 23:31.827
I saw him run under.

23:31.910 --> 23:33.537
{\an1}What kind of cheese
are you using?

23:33.620 --> 23:35.330
{\an3}Camembert.

23:35.413 --> 23:36.957
{\an1}Cam...?

23:37.040 --> 23:38.125
Steve, can you believe?

23:38.208 --> 23:40.961
