cheese to catch a mouse.

23:41.044 --> 23:41.837
Well, why not?

23:41.920 --> 23:44.339
{\an3}After all, it is
a Beverly Hills mouse.

23:44.423 --> 23:48.218
♪ Keep on pushing, baby,
please don't stop ♪

23:48.301 --> 23:49.845
Here you go.

23:49.928 --> 23:52.180
